            <p><div class="content_para"><p>This is the current release of the guideline.</p>
<p>This guideline updates a previous version: National Collaborating Centre for Chronic Conditions. Type 1 diabetes in adults. National clinical guideline for diagnosis and management in primary and secondary care. London (UK): Royal College of Physicians; 2004. 171 p. [382 references]</p>
<p>This guideline meets NGC's 2013 (revised) inclusion criteria.</p></div></p>
