            </ul>
                    <h4>UMLS Concepts <a href="/web/20180712204155/https://www.guideline.gov/help-and-about/search-browse/umls-concepts" class="what-is">(what is this?)</a></h4>
                <div class="field">
                    <h5 class="field-label">ICD9CM</h5>
                    <div class="field-content">
<a href="/web/20180712204155/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0007222&amp;fLockTerm=Cardiovascular+disease%2c+unspecified">Cardiovascular disease, unspecified</a>
 (429.2), <a href="/web/20180712204155/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0375114&amp;fLockTerm=Diabetes+mellitus+without+mention+of+complication%2c+type+I+%5bjuvenile+type%5d%2c+not+stated+as+uncontrolled">Diabetes mellitus without mention of complication, type I [juvenile type], not stated as uncontrolled</a>
 (250.01), <a href="/web/20180712204155/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0020615&amp;fLockTerm=Hypoglycemia%2c+unspecified">Hypoglycemia, unspecified</a>
 (251.2), <a href="/web/20180712204155/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0199782&amp;fLockTerm=Injection+of+insulin">Injection of insulin</a>
 (99.17), <a href="/web/20180712204155/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0030275&amp;fLockTerm=Pancreatic+transplant%2c+not+otherwise+specified">Pancreatic transplant, not otherwise specified</a>
 (52.80)                    </div>
